subject: Basketball
College Athletics
lead_paragraph: The highly regarded Southern California guard Jacki Gemelos has suffered another season-ending knee injury. Gemelos tore the anterior cruciate ligament and meniscus in her left knee during a workout. Previously, she tore the A.C.L. in her right knee twice.
